lead_paragraph: Chanda Rubin defeated Germany’s Martina Muller, 6-3, 6-0, yesterday to reach the second round of the Fortis Championships in Luxembourg. Rubin, ranked 342nd in the world, last won at Cincinnati in the summer of 2005, but she needed only 53 minutes to beat the 37th-ranked Muller.
